Name: Stormquell (I)
Desc: At the start of every Cycle, allies whose current HP percentage is greater than <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> increase their ATK by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> for <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak></color> turn(s).

Challenge.Name: Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Have no downed characters
